claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table outlining contraindications and precautions for different 2022–23 influenza vaccine platforms (egg-based IIV4 and LAIV4, cell-culture ccIIV4, and recombinant RIV4) in individuals with a history of severe allergic reaction to influenza vaccines. The table provides guidance on contraindications and precautions related to vaccine allergies but contains no information on antigenic match or strain selection, so it does not support the claim.
